{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Forge Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #b30000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #e09999; /* Lighter shade of red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background */\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        #hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        #games .game-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .game-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n        .game-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(179, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n        .game-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .game-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n        .game-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        #about, #contact {\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        #about p, #contact p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n        #contact input,\n        #contact textarea {\n            padding: 12px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        #contact input::placeholder,\n        #contact textarea::placeholder {\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n        }\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            nav {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                margin: 5px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Crimson Forge Studios</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"#games\">Games</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Unleash Your Imagination</h2>\n            <p>Crafting immersive worlds and unforgettable gaming experiences. Where passion meets pixels.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"games\">\n            <h2>Our Latest Titles</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-list\">\n                <div class=\"game-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/b30000/ffffff?text=Game+1+Artwork\" alt=\"Game 1 Artwork\">\n                    <h3>Chronicles of Eldoria</h3>\n                    <p>Embark on an epic fantasy quest filled with magic, monsters, and ancient secrets.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e09999/ffffff?text=Game+2+Artwork\" alt=\"Game 2 Artwork\">\n                    <h3>Nebula Drift</h3>\n                    <p>Soar through uncharted galaxies in this thrilling space exploration and combat simulator.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/b30000/ffffff?text=Game+3+Artwork\" alt=\"Game 3 Artwork\">\n                    <h3>Steel & Shadow</h3>\n                    <p>A dark, atmospheric stealth-action game set in a dystopian metropolis.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Crimson Forge</h2>\n            <p>Crimson Forge Studios is a passionate team of game developers dedicated to creating high-quality, engaging, and memorable gaming experiences. Founded in 2020, our mission is to push the boundaries of interactive entertainment, blending innovative gameplay with captivating storytelling. We believe in the power of games to transport players to new worlds and forge lasting connections.</p>\n            <p>We are driven by a love for gaming and a commitment to excellence. Join us on our journey as we continue to build the games of your dreams.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have a question, a partnership idea, or just want to say hello? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Forge Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent! Thank you for contacting Crimson Forge Studios.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}